    ],
    "text": "On the night of 07.07.2026, officers attached to the Police Special Task Force Headquarters Camp conducted a raid within the Enderamulla Police Division following a tip-off and arrested a suspect found in possession of 2 kilograms and 325 grams of heroin. The suspect was subsequently handed over to the Enderamulla Police Station for further legal action.",
    "fonts": [
