    "text": "Subsequent investigations and the interrogation of the initial suspect led to the arrest of a second individual allegedly involved in drug trafficking in the Kerawalapitiya area. During the operation, officers also took into police custody a jeep and a mobile phone believed to be connected to the offence.",
